{
  "info": {
    "name": "KOSMO SDD - Pipeline Completo",
    "description": "Flujo completo de Spec-Driven Development en KOSMO.\n\nIncluye: Auth PKCE, Proyectos, Descubrimiento (9 secciones), Features (sugerir desde idea del usuario + creacion unitaria + IA devuelve sugerencias sin persistir), Requisitos EARS (6 categorias, IDs secuenciales, Discovery completo en prompt) y pipeline SDD.\n\nReglas:\n- 4.1: El usuario escribe una idea. La IA devuelve titulo formal + descripcion (NO persiste). Usar 4.2 para confirmar.\n- Features solo se pueden editar/mejorar en estado Borrador (409 si estan Aprobadas)\n- Requisitos solo se generan para features Aprobadas (409 si estan en Borrador)\n- PUT de requisitos solo actualiza categorias enviadas; el resto se preserva.\n- POST /features/generate y /suggest-from-idea retornan sugerencias NO persistidas. Usar 4.2 para crear una a una.\n\nEjecutar las requests en orden estricto dentro de cada carpeta.\n\nPre-requisitos:\n- Base URL: http://localhost:8000\n- Servidor corriendo: uv run uvicorn kosmo.infrastructure.api.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000\n- Docker con PostgreSQL y Redis corriendo\n- .env con LLM_PROVIDER=deepseek o noop",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "access_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "email", "value": "demo@kosmo.app", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "password", "value": "Demo1234!Secure", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "spec_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "project_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "feature_id", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Auth (PKCE)",
      "description": "Flujo de autenticacion completo con PKCE. Ejecutar en orden: Register -> Authorize -> Token.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1.1 Registrar usuario",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "function setVar(key, value) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(key, value);",
                  "    if (pm.environment && pm.environment.name) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set(key, value);",
                  "    }",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('201 (creado) o 409 (ya existe)', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect([201, 409]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    setVar('user_id', body.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.2 Autorizar (PKCE) - Obtener authorization_code",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "function setVar(key, value) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(key, value);",
                  "    if (pm.environment && pm.environment.name) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set(key, value);",
                  "    }",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('201 Created', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(201); });",
                  "var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "setVar('authorization_code', body.authorization_code);",
                  "pm.test('authorization_code presente', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(body.authorization_code).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "function base64url(wordArray) {",
                  "    return CryptoJS.enc.Base64.stringify(wordArray)",
                  "        .replace(/\\+/g, '-')",
                  "        .replace(/\\//g, '_')",
                  "        .replace(/=+$/, '');",
                  "}",
                  "var verifier = base64url(CryptoJS.lib.WordArray.random(48));",
                  "var challenge = base64url(CryptoJS.SHA256(verifier));",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('code_verifier', verifier);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('code_challenge', challenge);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\",\n  \"code_challenge\": \"{{code_challenge}}\",\n  \"code_challenge_method\": \"S256\",\n  \"scopes\": [\"read\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/authorize",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "authorize"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.3 Intercambiar codigo por tokens JWT",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "function setVar(key, value) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(key, value);",
                  "    if (pm.environment && pm.environment.name) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set(key, value);",
                  "    }",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "setVar('access_token', body.access.token);",
                  "setVar('refresh_token', body.refresh.token);",
                  "pm.test('token_type Bearer', function () { pm.expect(body.token_type).to.eql('Bearer'); });",
                  "pm.test('access.token presente', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(body.access.token).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"grant_type\": \"authorization_code\",\n  \"code\": \"{{authorization_code}}\",\n  \"code_verifier\": \"{{code_verifier}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/token",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "token"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Proyectos",
      "description": "Gestion de proyectos: crear, listar y obtener. Ejecutar en orden.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "2.1 Crear Proyecto",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "function setVar(key, value) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(key, value);",
                  "    if (pm.environment && pm.environment.name) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set(key, value);",
                  "    }",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('201 Created', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(201); });",
                  "var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "setVar('project_id', body.id);",
                  "pm.test('project_id asignado', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(body.id).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('fase inicial = descubrimiento', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(body.current_phase).to.eql('descubrimiento');",
                  "});",
                  "console.log('[OK] Proyecto creado:', body.id, '-', body.name);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Sistema de Gestion de Inventario\",\n  \"description\": \"Un sistema que permite a pequenas empresas gestionar su inventario en tiempo real, controlar stock, generar reportes y recibir alertas de bajo inventario.\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "projects"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2.2 Listar Proyectos",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var data = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Array de proyectos', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(data).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});",
                  "console.log('[OK] Proyectos encontrados:', data.length);",
                  "data.forEach(function(p) {",
                  "    console.log('  -', p.name, '| fase:', p.current_phase, '| status:', p.status);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "projects"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2.3 Obtener Proyecto",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "console.log('[OK] Proyecto:', body.name);",
                  "console.log('  Fase:', body.current_phase);",
                  "console.log('  Estado:', body.status);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "projects", "{{project_id}}"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Descubrimiento (Fase 1)",
      "description": "Fase de Descubrimiento: genera el documento de 9 secciones a partir de la descripcion del proyecto. Ejecutar en orden.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "3.1 Generar Discovery con IA",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "function setVar(key, value) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(key, value);",
                  "    if (pm.environment && pm.environment.name) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set(key, value);",
                  "    }",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    setVar('spec_id', body.id);",
                  "    console.log('[OK] Discovery generado. Secciones:');",
                  "    Object.keys(body).forEach(function(key) {",
                  "        if (body[key] && body[key].length > 0) {",
                  "            console.log('  -', key, ':', body[key].substring(0, 50) + '...');",
                  "        }",
                  "    });",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('[ERROR]', pm.response.text());",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/discovery/generate",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "projects", "{{project_id}}", "discovery", "generate"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3.2 Obtener Discovery",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('[OK] Discovery actual:');",
                  "    console.log('  Vision:', body.vision ? body.vision.substring(0, 60) + '...' : 'vacio');",
                  "    console.log('  Alcance:', body.scope ? body.scope.substring(0, 60) + '...' : 'vacio');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/discovery",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "projects", "{{project_id}}", "discovery"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3.3 Actualizar Discovery (editor)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('[OK] Discovery actualizado:');",
                  "    console.log('  Vision:', body.vision ? body.vision.substring(0, 80) + '...' : 'vacio');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"vision\": \"Plataforma web de gestion de inventario para pequenas y medianas empresas que necesitan controlar su stock en tiempo real.\",\n  \"scope\": \"Incluye gestion de productos, control de stock, alertas de inventario bajo y reportes basicos. No incluye integracion con ERP externos ni facturacion electronica.\",\n  \"business_rules\": \"Solo los administradores pueden modificar precios y eliminar productos. Los operadores pueden registrar entradas y salidas de inventario.\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/discovery",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "projects", "{{project_id}}", "discovery"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Caracteristicas (Fase 2)",
      "description": "Gestion de caracteristicas del proyecto. Las features inician vacias. La creacion es estrictamente unitaria (una a una). La IA sugiere pero NO persiste. Mejoras IA solo disponibles en estado Borrador.\n\nFlujo recomendado (nuevo):\n1. 4.1 Sugerir desde idea — El usuario escribe una idea (ej: Alertas de stock bajo). La IA devuelve titulo formal + descripcion detallada (NO persiste)\n2. 4.2 Crear Feature — Confirmar la sugerencia de 4.1 enviando titulo y descripcion, o crear una manual (persiste)\n\nFlujo alternativo (legacy):\n3. 4.3 Generar sugerencias IA desde contexto (read-only, no persiste)\n4. 4.2 Crear una a una las features deseadas\n5. 4.7 Mejorar con IA (solo Borrador, 409 si Aprobada)\n6. 4.8 Aplicar mejora (solo Borrador)\n7. 4.6 Toggle a Aprobada para habilitar Fase 3 (Requisitos)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "4.1 Sugerir Desde Idea del Usuario (NO persiste — usar 4.2 para confirmar)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('[OK] Sugerencia generada desde idea:');",
                  "    console.log('  Titulo:', body.title);",
                  "    console.log('  Descripcion:', body.description.substring(0, 120) + '...');",
                  "    console.log('  [Frontend debe decidir: Cancelar o Confirmar con 4.2]');",
                  "    console.log('  [Para confirmar, copia title y description en el body de 4.2]');",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('[ERROR]', pm.response.text());",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"idea\": \"Alertas de stock bajo con notificaciones automaticas por email\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/features/suggest-from-idea",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "projects", "{{project_id}}", "features", "suggest-from-idea"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4.2 Crear Feature (Confirmar sugerencia o manual)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('201 Created', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(201); });",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('feature_id', body.id);",
                  "    console.log('[OK] Feature creada:', body.id);",
                  "    console.log('  Titulo:', body.title);",
                  "    console.log('  Status:', body.status);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Gestion de alertas de stock bajo\",\n  \"description\": \"Permite a los administradores configurar umbrales minimos de stock por producto y recibir notificaciones automaticas por email cuando el inventario alcance niveles criticos, facilitando la reposicion oportuna y evitando quiebres de stock.\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/features",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "projects", "{{project_id}}", "features"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4.3 Generar Sugerencias IA desde Discovery (NO persiste — read-only)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('[OK] Sugerencias generadas (NO persistidas):', data.total);",
                  "    data.features.forEach(function(f) {",
                  "        console.log('  - [Sugerencia]', f.title);",
                  "    });",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('[ERROR]', pm.response.text());",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/features/generate",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "projects", "{{project_id}}", "features", "generate"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4.4 Listar Features",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var data = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('total es numero', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(data.total).to.be.a('number');",
                  "});",
                  "console.log('[OK] Total features:', data.total);",
                  "data.features.forEach(function(f) {",
                  "    var icon = f.status === 'aprobada' ? '[OK]' : '[~]';",
                  "    console.log(' ', icon, f.title);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/features",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "projects", "{{project_id}}", "features"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4.5 Sugerir Features Alternativas (IA)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('[OK] Sugerencias recibidas:', data.suggestions.length);",
                  "    data.suggestions.forEach(function(s, i) {",
                  "        console.log('  ' + (i+1) + '.', s.title);",
                  "        console.log('     ', s.description.substring(0, 70) + '...');",
                  "    });",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('[ERROR]', pm.response.text());",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/features/suggest",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "projects", "{{project_id}}", "features", "suggest"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4.6 Toggle Status (Borrador <-> Aprobada)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "console.log('[OK] Estado alternado; nuevo status:', body.status);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/features/{{feature_id}}/status",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "features", "{{feature_id}}", "status"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4.7 Mejorar Feature con IA (SOLO Borrador — 409 si Aprobada)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var body = pm.response.json();",
